summary: Gold lockpics carryweight and dragon souls
descriptionHtml:
unlimited carryweight, unlimited gold, unlimited lockpicks, a few dragonsouls
I was searching around nexus and I couldn't find a batch that only added those four items in large quantities +9999999 for gold and lockpicks, +99999 to carryweight item capacity however else you might say it, and +500 dragon souls every time you type in the command bat bat
useful tip the button to pull up command prompt on most standard keyboards is above tab and below esc
author: AnKorzz
